(215,'Palun tutvuge alljärgnevaga, et veenduda, et teie taskid on õigesti formuleeritud:\r\n<h2>Kriteeriumide koostamise kontrollnimekiri</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Selge kõigile osapooltele</li>\r\n  <li>Seda saab testida või kontrollida</li>\r\n  <li>Kriteerium kas läbib või ei läbi (näiteks ei saa olla 50% täidetud)</li>\r\n  <li>Keskendub tulemusele, mitte sellele, kuidas tulemus saavutatakse</li>\r\n  <li>Nii konkreetne kui võimalik (kiire lehe laadimisaeg vs. 3-sekundiline lehe laadimisaeg)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Millised on mõned näited aktsepteerimiskriteeriumidest?</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>As a customer I can view my shopping cart:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>PayPal, Google Pay, Apple Pay, and all major credit cards can be used to complete the transaction</li>\r\n  <li>Shopping cart item(s) are displayed</li>\r\n  <li>Items can be deleted from the shopping cart</li>\r\n  <li>User is prompted to log in if they aren’t already</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>As a customer I want to get an email every month about my water cost:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>I can see the amount due</li>\r\n  <li>I can see the due date</li>\r\n  <li>I can see the a possible late fee</li>\r\n  <li>I can click a link to sign in and pay easily</li>\r\n  <li>I can see how I can contact the office with questions or concerns</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>As a patient I want to be able to fill my pre-appointment paperwork online:</h3>\r\n<ul><li><strong>Given</strong> that I’m an existing health center patient,\r\n<strong>When</strong> I schedule an appointment online,\r\n<strong>Then</strong> I will receive the fillable pre-appointment paperwork on my email</li></ul>',3,1,'2024-10-16 19:43:36',0),
(216,'',1,12,'2024-10-16 20:40:03',0),
