(331,'Henno Täht lisas õpilasele Joel-Martin Riive tagasisideks: \'HTML validation errors found:\n\nConsider avoiding viewport values that prevent users from resizing documents.\nTrailing slash on void elements has no effect and interacts badly with unquoted attribute values.\nTrailing slash on void elements has no effect and interacts badly with unquoted attribute values.\nTrailing slash on void elements has no effect and interacts badly with unquoted attribute values.\'',10,1,'2024-10-24 16:47:07',1),
(332,'Henno Täht muutis õpilase Joel-Martin Riive hinnet:  -> MA',10,1,'2024-10-24 16:47:07',1),
