(457,'Henno Täht lisas õpilasele Oleksandr Ovsiienko tagasisideks: \'Again, I only see an empty repo. You need to clone this repo to your computer, add a file which includes at least one function, condition, loop and variable. The code must be related to information (IT management, if you need a more specific topic)\'',1,1,'2024-10-29 11:20:46',1),
