(9,39,3,'A','https://github.com/henno/todo-app/commit/769a20b6d3474421dcef8813119d0c62dadf9265','[]','1970-01-01 00:00:00',NULL,NULL),
(9,40,3,'MA','https://github.com/Sigmartreumann/issue-tracker','[{\"name\":\"Sigmar Treumann\",\"comment\":\"https:\\/\\/my.moqups.com\\/dashboard\\/projects\\/MhPqkDlYos\\/filter\\/all\",\"createdAt\":\"2024-11-27 21:22:21\"},{\"name\":\"Henno T\\u00e4ht\",\"comment\":\"Proovides projekti allakloonida ja k\\u00e4ima panna, sain brauseris ette lehe, kus saab juba otsida pileteid, lahendusi lisada ja probleeme sulgeda ja palju muud. Aga sinu esimene kasutajalugu oli ju \\\"As a user (employee or external client), I want to log in to the help desk system so that I can securely access features like creating and tracking issues\\\", mille tingimused olid:\\nKui e-post ja parool on sisestatud, saab vajutada sisselogimise nuppu.\\nKui andmed on valed, kuvatakse teade \\\"Vale e-post v\\u00f5i parool\\\".\\nKui v\\u00e4ljad on t\\u00fchjad, kuvatakse teade \\\"Kohustuslik v\\u00e4li puudub\\\".\\nKui e-post ja parool on \\u00f5iged, kontrollib s\\u00fcsteem neid andmebaasis.\\nKui parool vastab andmebaasis salvestatule, toimub sisselogimine.\\nKui andmed on \\u00f5iged, suunatakse kasutaja t\\u00f6\\u00f6lauale.\\nKui kasutaja logib sisse, luuakse turvaline sessioon.\\nKui sessioon on aegunud, peab kasutaja uuesti sisse logima.\\nKui kasutaja proovib avada kaitstud lehte ilma sisse logimata, suunatakse ta sisselogimise lehele.\\n\\nLisaks on kehtestuss\\u00f5num \\\"Add files via upload\\\", mis rikub 3. tingimust. Lisaks pole esimene kasutajalugu suletud olekus.\",\"createdAt\":\"2024-11-28 00:37:46\"},{\"name\":\"Sigmar Treumann\",\"comment\":\"n\\u00fc\\u00fcd peaks k\\u00f5ik olema \\u00f5ieti.\",\"createdAt\":\"2024-12-05 07:45:32\"},{\"name\":\"Henno T\\u00e4ht\",\"comment\":\"Selles projektis peab olema lisaks Initial commitile ainult \\u00fcksainus kehtestus ja selle s\\u00f5num peab olema:\\n```\\nAs a user (employee or external client), I want to log in to the help desk system so that I can securely access features like creating and tracking issues\\n\\nCloses #1\\n```\",\"createdAt\":\"2024-12-06 17:57:06\"},{\"name\":\"Henno T\\u00e4ht\",\"comment\":\"Endiselt ei ole n\\u00e4ha \\u00fchte kehtestust, mille s\\u00f5num oleks `As a user (employee or external client), I want to log in to the help desk system so that I can securely access features like creating and tracking issues` ja on hoopis v\\u00e4ga palju muude nimedega kehtestusi: [https:\\/\\/github.com\\/Sigmartreumann\\/issue-tracker\\/commits\\/main\\/](https:\\/\\/github.com\\/Sigmartreumann\\/issue-tracker\\/commits\\/main\\/)\",\"createdAt\":\"2024-12-19 22:56:44\"}]','1970-01-01 00:00:00',NULL,NULL),
