(11,19,3,'MA','https://github.com/OlgaOrl/Tree-Fungi-Identifier/commit/78a5f289bec27325147242ada7cecbff6bd778d7','[{\"comment\":\"Kasutajalugu oli \\\"as a user I can filter fungi\\\", aga ma ei n\\u00e4e v\\u00f5imalust seda teha\",\"name\":\"Henno T\\u00e4ht\",\"createdAt\":\"1970-01-01 00:00:00\"},{\"name\":\"Henno T\\u00e4ht\",\"comment\":\"Iga kehtestus main harus peaks sisaldama mitte rohkem ega v\\u00e4hem, kui t\\u00e4pselt ainult vastava kasutajaloo sisu. Siit on n\\u00e4ha, et on tehtud lisakehtestusi: https:\\/\\/github.com\\/OlgaOrl\\/Tree-Fungi-Identifier\\/commits\\/main\\/ Tee uus repo (squashimine v\\u00f5taks ilmselt kauem aega).\",\"createdAt\":\"2024-11-28 00:12:27\"},{\"name\":\"Olga Orlova\",\"comment\":\"muutsin \\u00e4ra\",\"createdAt\":\"2024-11-28 10:16:19\"},{\"name\":\"Henno T\\u00e4ht\",\"comment\":\"T\\u00e4psustan, mida eelmise kommentaariga m\\u00f5tlesin:\\n\\nJ\\u00e4rgmisi kehtestusi ei tohi eksisteerida, sest nad ei ole 1:1 seotud \\u00fchegi kasutajalooga:\\n1. Add a filter function (the site of growth, lifespan and the shape of the fruiting body) to add.js, seed.js, home.handlebars and schema.prisma.\\n2. Change schema.prisma, seed.js and app.js for working with MySql.\\n3. Change home.handlebars and upgrade package-lock.json\\n\\nJ\\u00e4rgmisi kehtestusi peaks olema 1, mitte 2:\\nAs a user, I can filter a tree fungi list by site of growth, lifespan, and shape\",\"createdAt\":\"2024-11-28 13:02:51\"},{\"name\":\"Olga Orlova\",\"comment\":\"Kas n\\u00fc\\u00fcd on ok?\",\"createdAt\":\"2024-12-02 16:54:14\"},{\"name\":\"Henno T\\u00e4ht\",\"comment\":\"HTML \\u00fcldstruktuur (`<doctype>`, `<html>`, `<head>`) peab olema ainult layout failis, mitte vaatefailis ka, sest muidu tuleb neid lehele topelt.\",\"createdAt\":\"2024-12-03 23:26:34\"},{\"name\":\"Henno T\\u00e4ht\",\"comment\":\"Projekt ei l\\u00e4he k\\u00e4ima:\\n\\n```\\n\\u276f git clone git@github.com:OlgaOrl\\/Tree-Fungi-Identifier.git\\nCloning into \'Tree-Fungi-Identifier\'...\\nEnter passphrase for key \'\\/Users\\/henno\\/.ssh\\/id_rsa\':\\nremote: Enumerating objects: 30, done.\\nremote: Counting objects: 100% (30\\/30), done.\\nremote: Compressing objects: 100% (23\\/23), done.\\nremote: Total 30 (delta 5), reused 23 (delta 3), pack-reused 0 (from 0)\\nReceiving objects: 100% (30\\/30), 41.77 KiB | 497.00 KiB\\/s, done.\\nResolving deltas: 100% (5\\/5), done.\\n\\u276f cd Tree-Fungi-Identifier\\/\\n\\u276f npm install\\n(node:456) ExperimentalWarning: CommonJS module \\/opt\\/homebrew\\/lib\\/node_modules\\/npm\\/node_modules\\/debug\\/src\\/node.js is loading ES Module \\/opt\\/homebrew\\/lib\\/node_modules\\/npm\\/node_modules\\/supports-color\\/index.js using require().\\nSupport for loading ES Module in require() is an experimental feature and might change at any time\\n(Use `node --trace-warnings ...` to show where the warning was created)\\nnpm warn deprecated inflight@1.0.6: This module is not supported, and leaks memory. Do not use it. Check out lru-cache if you want a good and tested way to coalesce async requests by a key value, which is much more comprehensive and powerful.\\nnpm warn deprecated @npmcli\\/move-file@1.1.2: This functionality has been moved to @npmcli\\/fs\\nnpm warn deprecated npmlog@6.0.2: This package is no longer supported.\\nnpm warn deprecated rimraf@3.0.2: Rimraf versions prior to v4 are no longer supported\\nnpm warn deprecated are-we-there-yet@3.0.1: This package is no longer supported.\\nnpm warn deprecated glob@7.2.3: Glob versions prior to v9 are no longer supported\\nnpm warn deprecated glob@7.2.3: Glob versions prior to v9 are no longer supported\\nnpm warn deprecated glob@7.2.3: Glob versions prior to v9 are no longer supported\\nnpm warn deprecated gauge@4.0.4: This package is no longer supported.\\n\\nadded 295 packages, and audited 296 packages in 2s\\n\\n50 packages are looking for funding\\n  run `npm fund` for details\\n\\n2 moderate severity vulnerabilities\\n\\nTo address all